  m_Name: NeighborJournal_20
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 38
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #20 \u2014 \u0110\xEAm cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng"
  category: 3
  content: "T\xF4i l\xE0m vi\u1EC7c \u1EDF Motel n\xE0y 6 n\u0103m. \u0110\xEAm cu\u1ED1i
    c\xF9ng, ph\xF2ng 12 g\u1ECDi l\xEAn \u2014 kh\xE1ch b\u1EA3o th\u1EA5y h\xE0ng
    x\xF3m ph\xF2ng 11 'kh\xF4ng \u1ED5n'. T\xF4i l\xEAn ki\u1EC3m tra, anh ta \u0111ang
    g\u1EA7m v\xE0 lao v\xE0o t\xF4i. T\xF4i ch\u1EA1y, kh\xF3a c\u1EEDa v\u0103n
    ph\xF2ng. Su\u1ED1t \u0111\xEAm nghe ti\u1EBFng \u0111\u1EADp c\u1EEDa. Bu\u1ED5i
    s\xE1ng, im \u1EAFng. T\xF4i m\u1EDF c\u1EEDa \u2014 h\xE0nh lang \u0111\u1EA7y
    m\xE1u, kh\xF4ng ai c\xF2n. T\xF4i l\u1EA5y ch\xECa kh\xF3a xe kh\xE1ch, b\u1ECF
    \u0111i. Ch\xFAc ai \u0111\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c may m\u1EAFn."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
